A pile of books, carelessly discarded.
The books lay piled atop each other with little in the way of rhyme or reason, as if someone was interrupted while in the process of returning them to their place.
A wooden-framed painting hangs on the wall, depicting a hazy scene from the ancient past. A floating city is visible in the sky, hanging above majestic towers.
This model represents what Faerun would look like from a great distance.
